        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[[哈欠]#晚上睡不着和熬夜有什么区别# 熬夜的危害小卫就不说了（再说也阻止不了大家继续熬夜[doge]）那熬夜和失眠有啥区别？熬夜是指睡得晚并且睡得少。[星星]睡...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[哈欠]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_dahaqi-b1824d3d83.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%99%9A%E4%B8%8A%E7%9D%A1%E4%B8%8D%E7%9D%80%E5%92%8C%E7%86%AC%E5%A4%9C%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%99%9A%E4%B8%8A%E7%9D%A1%E4%B8%8D%E7%9D%80%E5%92%8C%E7%86%AC%E5%A4%9C%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#晚上睡不着和熬夜有什么区别#</span></a> 熬夜的危害小卫就不说了（再说也阻止不了大家继续熬夜<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>）那熬夜和失眠有啥区别？<br><br>熬夜是指睡得晚并且睡得少。<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>睡得晚<br>每个人都有一个相对固定的入睡时间点，晚于这个时间半个小时及以上，就可称为晚睡。<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>睡得少<br>一般来说，成年人的最佳睡眠时长是7-9小时，但当我们晚睡且睡眠时长不足六小时时，就算熬夜了。非要说一个具体时间点的话<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[思考]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_sikao-ff9602dd08.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>从内分泌角度而言，晚上11点后睡觉就算熬夜。<br><br>而失眠属于被动型熬夜，有以下几个特点👇🏻<br>1️⃣入睡困难，入睡时间超过30分钟；<br>2️⃣睡眠时间少于6小时；<br>3️⃣睡眠质量差，醒来次数多，容易早醒；<br>4️⃣白天容易出现头晕疲劳、注意力不足，思睡等。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a> （科普中国）<br><br>周五了，今晚打算几点睡？<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[哈欠]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_dahaqi-b1824d3d83.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <a href="http://t.cn/A6lIiIAi" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
