            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%8C%97%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%80%E5%90%AF%E8%87%B3%E5%86%B7%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB%E5%8D%97%E6%96%B9%E6%96%AD%E5%B4%96%E5%BC%8F%E9%99%8D%E6%B8%A9%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%8C%97%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%80%E5%90%AF%E8%87%B3%E5%86%B7%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB%E5%8D%97%E6%96%B9%E6%96%AD%E5%B4%96%E5%BC%8F%E9%99%8D%E6%B8%A9%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#北方开启至冷时刻南方断崖式降温#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[揣手]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/af/2022_chuaishou_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】小卫终于可以宠幸还没穿过的大棉袄、花秋裤了[磕到了] <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E6%B0%94%E8%B1%A1%E5%8F%B0%E7%BB%A7%E7%BB%AD%E8%BF%9E%E5%8F%91%E5%AF%92%E6%BD%AE%E5%A4%A7%E9%A3%8E%E9%A2%84%E8%AD%A6%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E6%B0%94%E8%B1%A1%E5%8F%B0%E7%BB%A7%E7%BB%AD%E8%BF%9E%E5%8F%91%E5%AF%92%E6%BD%AE%E5%A4%A7%E9%A3%8E%E9%A2%84%E8%AD%A6%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#中央气象台继续连发寒潮大风预警#</span></a>。受寒潮影响，今天起，北方大部将开启持续一周左右的今冬至冷时刻，南方这两天也准备进入“急冻”模式🥶卫宝们要注意保暖！👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4979111974862853" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hku485rs9qj61zb1447wh02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/iQNqBZtwlx08aXf3w87e01041200dY0A0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1702631822&amp;ssig=OjWYbJzSYF&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/TY3dnY5glx08aXf3fKGI010412007i0x0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1702631822&amp;ssig=4fdhSVbXtL&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/iJpTN1ZWlx08aXf36Iys010412004vrS0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1702631822&amp;ssig=ARSzyp5RFr&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4979111974862853" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
