        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【[泪]娃都生完了，怎么肚子还这么大！】生完娃后的丹丹医生，因为腹直肌分离，原本平坦的肚子挂了个悬浮的“大皮球”，跟怀孕的闺蜜7、8个月的肚子一样大！紧致...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[泪]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_lei-4cdf6ee412.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>娃都生完了，怎么肚子还这么大！】生完娃后的丹丹医生，因为腹直肌分离，原本平坦的肚子挂了个悬浮的“大皮球”，跟怀孕的闺蜜7、8个月的肚子一样大！紧致分明的马甲线，松到能插进8指，直捣肠道......尽管尝试了很多治疗，都不能将肚皮恢复到以前。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[裂开]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fc_liekai-9df295d44f.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>看完这些，是不是“劝退”了不少未婚未育的姐妹？丹丹医生却说——我不后悔生娃，但我没想到怀孕的过程也如此重要。生育问题就摆在眼前，我们要权衡之后，做出属于你自己最正确的选择。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[许愿星]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/a8/2022_WishingStar_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>当你下班回到家，娃追着你嘻嘻哈哈，不断地对你说“妈妈我爱你”，你闻着娃身上独有的香味，回一句妈妈也爱你时，会不会觉得，孩子就是上天带给你最好的礼物？<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[抱一抱]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/co_a1hug-f3910d0e88.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4978895905292361" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">深圳卫健委的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/a8bfee30gy1hktfrxo54hj20vu0hwase.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/NM4jckJggx08aWiNBvPG01041203DXDr0E020.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1702631833&amp;ssig=LV4Bw3BIhH&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/0Kj1HCnAgx08aWiMHF3y01041201YQF60E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1702631833&amp;ssig=ec0yj3UH58&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/2FuFGnKYgx08aWiMPPbO01041201imVC0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1702631833&amp;ssig=zUUx2GdVGa&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4978895905292361" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
