        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[[二哈]#女子长期穿光腿神器导致迈不开腿# 光腿神器，不仅能伪装成光腿，还能伪装成更加修长完美的光腿，可最近，有人却戏谑它为“现代刑具”[喵喵] 咋回事？[星...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[二哈]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_erha-139d0e07bd.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E9%95%BF%E6%9C%9F%E7%A9%BF%E5%85%89%E8%85%BF%E7%A5%9E%E5%99%A8%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E8%BF%88%E4%B8%8D%E5%BC%80%E8%85%BF%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E9%95%BF%E6%9C%9F%E7%A9%BF%E5%85%89%E8%85%BF%E7%A5%9E%E5%99%A8%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E8%BF%88%E4%B8%8D%E5%BC%80%E8%85%BF%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#女子长期穿光腿神器导致迈不开腿#</span></a>  光腿神器，不仅能伪装成光腿，还能伪装成更加修长完美的光腿，可最近，有人却戏谑它为“现代刑具”<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[喵喵]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_miao-c1b3d563bd.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> 咋回事？<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>容易引起甲沟炎<br>甲沟炎是趾甲（指甲）周围的软组织被细菌、真菌感染而引起的炎症。脚部受力异常，比如平时喜欢穿紧身袜、尖头鞋，冬天爱穿光腿神器等，也会造成脚趾头向下弯曲过度，不断挤压摩擦，引起甲沟炎。<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>腿部血液会不循环<br>长期穿过紧的“光腿神器”，会导致脚踝部的压力较低，大腿的压力较高，抑制静脉血液的回流，阻碍静脉血液回流心脏，可能会出现腿肿、腿部沉重的情况。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[衰]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shuai-285d2d97c7.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（i深圳）<img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hktdlnxjgwj20u00h9whb.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
            <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 08:03:19 GMT</pubDate>
